function Start()

	actorClone = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(actorQuestgiverA)
	if (Hydra.ActorIsValid(actorClone)) then -- Always check that a clone actor exists before running script on it
		Hydra.QActorClearAnimSetOverride(actorClone) -- Clear the AnimSet Override from the source NPC
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(actorClone, actorQuestgiverB, "NPC_WALK", true)
		Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(actorClone, actorQuestgiverB)
		Hydra.QActorSetAnimSetOverride(actorClone, animsetSitCrossLegged)
		Hydra.QActorDeletePersonalClone(actorClone) -- End your queued actions with a QActorDeletePersonalClone so the clone is self-terminating
	end

end
